snippet.textDisplay: Thank you for stressing the importance of sleep! Sleep is vital 7-8 hours/ night! As my microbiology Professor said to us " Immunity is EVERYTHING!" Eat right, exercise moderately, and get 7-8 hours of sleep every night! 3 Keys to good health!
